text: Triangle of Sadness is a 2022 black comedy movie written and directed by Ruben Östlund. It stars Harris Dickinson, Charlbi Dean, Dolly de Leon, Zlatko Burić, Henrik Dorsin, Vicki Berlin, and Woody Harrelson. The movie is about a celebrity couple on a luxury cruise with rich guests. The movie had positive reviews. It received three nominations at the 95th Academy Awards, including Best Picture. ==References== Category:2022 comedy movies Category:2020s black comedy movies Category:Swedish comedy movies Category:German comedy movies Category:French comedy movies Category:British black comedy movies
